OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThe evening
OL,6,Fwill start mostly cloudy with some
OL,7,Fshowers, but drier weather over the
OL,8,FIsles will extend across Highland
OL,9,Fthrough the evening. Further cloud and
OL,10,Foutbreaks of rain, some heavy, will
OL,11,Fspread from the southwest from the
OL,12,Fearly hours.
OL,13,
OL,14,CFriday:FCloudy with outbreaks of
OL,15,Foccasionally heavy rain at first in
OL,16,Fthe morning. The rain will clear to
OL,17,Fscattered showers during the
OL,18,Fafternoon, with sunny intervals
OL,19,Fbreaking through.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
