OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FRain
OL,6,Fand showers clear north Saturday
OL,7,Fmorning to leave the rest of the
OL,8,Fweekend mainly dry with some sunshine.
OL,9,FMonday mostly dry warm and sunny but
OL,10,Fchance of rain later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
